{"tid":2444063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"外交部駐港公署：下周一起對接種中國疫苗簽證申請人提供便利","createTime":"2021-03-12T12:36:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T02:16:22.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"086a933a3012babe82cec276e5041b833ea655c4","tid":2444063,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"駐港公署下周一起對接種中國疫苗簽證申請人提供便利<br />\n<br />\n外交部駐港公署宣布，為有序恢復中外人員往來，由下星期一，對已經接種中國生產的新冠疫苗，並持疫苗接種證明的簽證申請人提供便利，在遞交申請時不再需要提供核酸檢測陰性證明、過去14天旅行軌跡和健康申報表，。<br />\n<br />\n受惠的對象包括，赴華從事各領域復工復產活動的外籍人員及家屬、因緊急人道主義需要，或持有效APEC商務旅行卡人員。。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382768&d=RYsttnILlo6fxd9QfZlXI8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=af610269\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382768</a>"},{"pid":"20603663314d040d7c21b76aa85f303b17598fe5","tid":2444063,"uid":78243,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T12:37:05.000Z","msg":"多撚謝﹐不了"},{"pid":"d52eef383683f4da01a30370cd6e60abeb2d05f9","tid":2444063,"uid":57214,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:10:35.000Z","msg":"翻譯：會勾難唔打支那針嘅外國人"},{"pid":"821986bfc299a6432702a10f9339f6f3df6e04e4","tid":2444063,"uid":57214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>翻譯：會刁難唔打支那針嘅外國人</blockquote>"},{"pid":"62c2dbda93d983d41c20b01df985ff6681b3ca62","tid":2444063,"uid":71092,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:07:41.000Z","msg":"地府免簽證待遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c01ba002cd35f2cf094e5664ba213f1edf51507","tid":2444063,"uid":41308,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T16:11: